What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Nasal Drug Delivery Market?

Market Analysis and Size

The rising patient preference for nasal drug delivery as a result of easy administration and better efficiency will act as major driver accelerating the global nasal drug delivery market’s growth rate. The rising adoption of self-administration practices will increase the demand for nasal drug delivery and further propel the market’s growth rate. Another significant factor resulting in the expansion of market is the rising focus on the development of smart/digital inhalers. Rapid urbanisation, changing lifestyle and rise in the level of disposable incomes in developing and developed countries will influence the growth rate of global nasal drug delivery market. The rise in the number of geriatric population and increase in the demand for home healthcare devices will flourish the growth rate of global nasal drug delivery market. Additionally, the increasing demand from emerging markets and the development of over-the-counter (OTC) drugs by various pharmaceutical companies will further expand the global nasal drug delivery market growth rate in the future.

